[%@lib add_const]
[|]
[`template<class T>] [br]
[`struct add_const;]
[|] [:en] If [`T] is a reference, function, or top-level const-qualified type,
    then [`type] denotes [`T], otherwise [`T const].
    [:zh_CN] 若 [`T] 为引用、函数或带有顶层 [`const] 限定的类型，则 [`type] 代表
    [`T]，否则为 [`T const]。
[-]

